  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Chronic hepatitis B virus infection is an important cause of morbidity and mortality.
      Tenofovir disoproxil fumarate and entecavir were licensed for the treatment of hepatitis B
      virus infection. In this study, the investigators will try to make comparison between
      Entecavir and Tenofovir and investigate the efficacy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
